text:
Katja Luraschi (born 6 January 1986 Riva del Garda) is an Italian volleyball player.
She played at the 2003 FIVB U18 Women's World Volleyball Championship winning a silver medal, and 2005 Women's European Volleyball Championship, winning a silver medal
She played for Volley Bergamo, Unet E-Work Busto Arsizio, Santeramo Sport, Robur Tiboni Urbino Volley.
